00:00:20.500 --> 00:00:26.000
They book. Their verified profile reaches the hotel before they do.

00:00:26.500 --> 00:00:32.000
They arrive. No forms. No waiting. Just welcome.

00:00:32.500 --> 00:00:38.000
One QR code. Instant room access.

00:00:38.500 --> 00:00:45.000
Verify Once. Travel Everywhere.

00:00:45.500 --> 00:00:50.000
ValtiqStay — Digital identity for luxury hospitality.
